                    <lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <orig>ьлвъ</orig> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_07958/">псат</w>  
                </ab>
            </div>
